zhoneIcmpEntry.name: zhoneIcmpEntry
zhoneIcmpEntry.description: Zhone ICMP Entry. This table augments the Routing Domain Table defined in comIpRD.mib.

zhIcmpInMsgs.name: zhIcmpInMsgs
zhIcmpInMsgs.description: The total number of ICMP messages which the entity received. Note that this counter includes all those counted by icmpInErrors.

zhIcmpInErrors.name: zhIcmpInErrors
zhIcmpInErrors.description: The number of ICMP messages which the entity received but determined as having ICMP-specific errors (bad ICMP checksums, bad length, etc.).

zhIcmpInDestUnreachs.name: zhIcmpInDestUnreachs
zhIcmpInDestUnreachs.description: The number of ICMP Destination Unreachable messages received.

zhIcmpInTimeExcds.name: zhIcmpInTimeExcds
zhIcmpInTimeExcds.description: The number of ICMP Time Exceeded messages received.

zhIcmpInParmProbs.name: zhIcmpInParmProbs
zhIcmpInParmProbs.description: The number of ICMP Parameter Problem messages received.

zhIcmpInSrcQuenchs.name: zhIcmpInSrcQuenchs
zhIcmpInSrcQuenchs.description: The number of ICMP Source Quench messages received.

zhIcmpInRedirects.name: zhIcmpInRedirects
zhIcmpInRedirects.description: The number of ICMP Redirect messages received.

zhIcmpInEchos.name: zhIcmpInEchos
zhIcmpInEchos.description: The number of ICMP Echo (request) messages received.

zhIcmpInEchoReps.name: zhIcmpInEchoReps
zhIcmpInEchoReps.description: The number of ICMP Echo Reply messages received.

zhIcmpInTimestamps.name: zhIcmpInTimestamps
zhIcmpInTimestamps.description: The number of ICMP Timestamp (request) messages received.

zhIcmpInTimestampReps.name: zhIcmpInTimestampReps
zhIcmpInTimestampReps.description: The number of ICMP Timestamp Reply messages received.

zhIcmpInAddrMasks.name: zhIcmpInAddrMasks
zhIcmpInAddrMasks.description: The number of ICMP Address Mask Request messages received.

zhIcmpInAddrMaskReps.name: zhIcmpInAddrMaskReps
zhIcmpInAddrMaskReps.description: The number of ICMP Address Mask Reply messages received.

zhIcmpOutMsgs.name: zhIcmpOutMsgs
zhIcmpOutMsgs.description: The total number of ICMP messages which this entity attempted to send. Note that this counter includes all those counted by icmpOutErrors.

zhIcmpOutErrors.name: zhIcmpOutErrors
zhIcmpOutErrors.description: The number of ICMP messages which this entity did not send due to problems discovered within ICMP such as a lack of buffers. This value should not include errors discovered outside the ICMP layer such as the inability of IP to route the resultant datagram. In some implementations there may be no types of error which contribute to this counter's value.

zhIcmpOutDestUnreachs.name: zhIcmpOutDestUnreachs
zhIcmpOutDestUnreachs.description: The number of ICMP Destination Unreachable messages sent.

zhIcmpOutTimeExcds.name: zhIcmpOutTimeExcds
zhIcmpOutTimeExcds.description: The number of ICMP Time Exceeded messages sent.

zhIcmpOutParmProbs.name: zhIcmpOutParmProbs
zhIcmpOutParmProbs.description: The number of ICMP Parameter Problem messages sent.

zhIcmpOutSrcQuenchs.name: zhIcmpOutSrcQuenchs
zhIcmpOutSrcQuenchs.description: The number of ICMP Source Quench messages sent.

zhIcmpOutRedirects.name: zhIcmpOutRedirects
zhIcmpOutRedirects.description: The number of ICMP Redirect messages sent. For a host, this object will always be zero, since hosts do not send redirects.

zhIcmpOutEchos.name: zhIcmpOutEchos
zhIcmpOutEchos.description: The number of ICMP Echo (request) messages sent.

zhIcmpOutEchoReps.name: zhIcmpOutEchoReps
zhIcmpOutEchoReps.description: The number of ICMP Echo Reply messages sent.

zhIcmpOutTimestamps.name: zhIcmpOutTimestamps
zhIcmpOutTimestamps.description: The number of ICMP Timestamp (request) messages sent.

zhIcmpOutTimestampReps.name: zhIcmpOutTimestampReps
zhIcmpOutTimestampReps.description: The number of ICMP Timestamp Reply messages sent.

zhIcmpOutAddrMasks.name: zhIcmpOutAddrMasks
zhIcmpOutAddrMasks.description: The number of ICMP Address Mask Request messages sent.

zhIcmpOutAddrMaskReps.name: zhIcmpOutAddrMaskReps
zhIcmpOutAddrMaskReps.description: The number of ICMP Address Mask Reply messages sent.
